<h1>Problem 235 - 2015 IMO, P2 of 6, N</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 9</h2>
<p>Find all positive integers \((a,b,c)\) such that \[ab-c,\quad bc-a,\quad ca-b\] are all powers of \(2\).<br><br>
<i>(A power of 2 is an integer of the form \(2^n\), where \(n\) is a nonnegative integer.)</i></p>
